Sentencas: Electrocatalytic effects on solid oxide ionic conductors in high temperature systems are discussed.
Titulo: ELECTROCATALYSIS AND MORPHOLOGY AT CATHODE MATERIALS FOR THE OXYGEN REACTION ON SOLID OXIDE IONIC CONDUCTORS

Sentencas: The oxygen electrode reaction on a solid electrolyte is depicted.
Titulo: ELECTROCATALYSIS AND MORPHOLOGY AT CATHODE MATERIALS FOR THE OXYGEN REACTION ON SOLID OXIDE IONIC CONDUCTORS

Sentencas: Possible oxygen reduction pathways are reviewed as a function of the nature of the electrode and electrolyte surface.
Titulo: ELECTROCATALYSIS AND MORPHOLOGY AT CATHODE MATERIALS FOR THE OXYGEN REACTION ON SOLID OXIDE IONIC CONDUCTORS

Sentencas: What is meant by electrocatalysis is defined and illustrated in two examples: the oxygen reduction on perovskites and on doped yttria-stabilized zirconia.
Titulo: ELECTROCATALYSIS AND MORPHOLOGY AT CATHODE MATERIALS FOR THE OXYGEN REACTION ON SOLID OXIDE IONIC CONDUCTORS
